<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-03-08T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-03-08T13:00:00-05:00" n="754" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d754">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/9073</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the Minister in Rumania</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_VCJ1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Vopicka</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-03-08T13:00:00-05:00">
                                        <hi rend="italic">March 8, 1918, 1 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>175. Your 32 [<hi rend="italic">47</hi>], 5th. Department has wired
                                Petrograd and Moscow to endeavor secure safe conduct military and
                                Red Cross mission. Department relies on your judgment as to leaving
                                Jassy but hopes situation may develop so that you can remain.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_PFL1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>